1. ``make clouds``
2. ``kubfiy start-all``

welcome
=======

kubify os oss, version: 9020.0.28

getting started
===============

local
=======

.. code-block:: bash

   $ [pip|conda] install kubify
   $ kubify --up
   $ kubify --start-all
   $ cd services[][] && kubify --start
   $ kubify --down

compatible with cloud providers
    * aws
    * gcp
    * azure

compatible with devops tools
    * terraform
    * terraform cdk
    * cloudformation
    * serverless framework
    * helm and kustomize

"if it works on my computer, it will work in the cloud"

cloud
=====

.. code-block:: bash

   $ make clouds
   $ make clouds-delete

